name: Baseball Texas Rangers ONESIE with custom name on back
description:
This adorable onesie will be made to order.
Just make sure to let me know what NAME you would like on the back.
Also, please make sure you send me the SIZE you need.
Please note the onesies run a little small, so please order a size up if you're unsure.

Onesies are 100% Cotton.
The print is a super soft print for your babies' comfort.

Size options are:
Newborn (5-8 lbs, 17-21 in)
0-3 months (8-12 lbs, 21-24 in)
3-6 months (12-16 lbs, 24-26 in)
6-9 months (16-20 lbs, 26-28 in)
12 months (20-24 lbs, 28-30 in)
18 months (24-28 lbs, 30-32 in)
24 months (28-32 lbs, 32-34 in)

Thank You for considering my item.
